{"tid":2321831,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有個中年同事 4字尾左右，好撚垃圾","createTime":"2020-12-11T23:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T15:46:51.000Z","uid":61823,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"70f1bd39f59fbf542eba5f6fe48a118745605f96","tid":2321831,"uid":61823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T23:34:53.000Z","msg":"份野係我個陣，佢同我一齊做野個陣就唔幫手，<br />\n份野係佢個陣，我做慢小小都黑撚哂面<br />\n<br />\n同佢做野又多野講<br />\n有日佢黑面太勁我頂唔順，我特登慢慢咁同佢做<br />\n佢就發撚哂脾氣咁<br />\n最大問題佢咩都覺得自己岩，講道理又唔聽，我可以點做？"},{"pid":"75941b908d0110536d6c48455846d90b64d1cfec","tid":2321831,"uid":256205,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T23:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTsUNV6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTsUNV6.jpg&h=f49534ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d04f18c712a87305ba95561e973a8dcf284d8a60","tid":2321831,"uid":61823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75941b908d0110536d6c48455846d90b64d1cfec","tid":2321831,"uid":256205,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T23:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTsUNV6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTsUNV6.jpg&h=f49534ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:00:19.000Z","msg":"直頭我心情"},{"pid":"2df270db9d8e1c09b3e8ed9c8347e4f367cbb086","tid":2321831,"uid":378059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:21:16.000Z","msg":"屌柒佢"},{"pid":"45fe4f4bfc0bbc822cf5dd10bfb8cbae85c7817f","tid":2321831,"uid":61823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2df270db9d8e1c09b3e8ed9c8347e4f367cbb086","tid":2321831,"uid":378059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:21:16.000Z","msg":"屌柒佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:31:52.000Z","msg":"屌過，反埋面"},{"pid":"4044e3aa11a1eb5c249af5e532bd34a0faa20328","tid":2321831,"uid":44815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"rep